title: Truly Nice Ass Collection [2-7]

Truly Nice Ass Collection [2-7]
-------------------------------

A masterful collection directed by Bryan Xin, for fans of great asses.

Took me a while to gather these because the seeding on most of them is very bad and dead on some. So I decided to make a collection and reupload. I only made the rip of Truly Nice Ass 3 because that's the only DVD I had, for the rest I thank various users and groups.

Unfortunately, I didn't manage to get my hands on the first movie in the series so if anyone has it or knows where to get it, please let me know in the comment section. I'd like to complete this collection.

I have personally checked and verified every file in this torrent and everything is 100% safe and working.

No thank you required, but I do ask of you to seed back at least to ratio of 1:1, so others can enjoy these splendid movies as well.

Happy downloading and seeding!
